00:12:38.560 --> 00:12:41.350
teach that? Until you get it.

00:12:41.360 --> 00:12:42.710
How long are you going to tell those

00:12:42.720 --> 00:12:45.590
same stories? Until you get it. Until it

00:12:45.600 --> 00:12:49.350
becomes Rhema in your life. Thank God for

00:12:49.350 --> 00:12:49.360
Rhema

00:12:49.360 --> 00:12:53.509
word. Thank God for words that

00:12:53.519 --> 00:12:56.790
become alive in you. When you study this

00:12:56.800 --> 00:12:59.590
Bible, when you get this word down in

00:12:59.600 --> 00:13:02.150
your heart and you get it into you

00:13:02.160 --> 00:13:04.629
that you are fully

00:13:04.639 --> 00:13:06.629
persuaded,

00:13:06.639 --> 00:13:09.350
you're no longer a believer. You're

00:13:09.360 --> 00:13:11.670
fully persuaded.

00:13:11.680 --> 00:13:13.910
You went from believing to fully

00:13:13.920 --> 00:13:15.509
persuaded

00:13:15.519 --> 00:13:17.990
that what God has promised, he's able

00:13:18.000 --> 00:13:20.870
also to perform it.

00:13:20.880 --> 00:13:23.670
I'm fully persuaded that my God is my

00:13:23.680 --> 00:13:25.509
provider.

00:13:25.519 --> 00:13:27.509
Well, my bank account may say something

00:13:27.519 --> 00:13:29.190
else. You go to the bank

00:13:29.200 --> 00:13:31.190
account. You say, I need a readout of

00:13:31.200 --> 00:13:32.550
my account. And they give you a

00:13:32.550 --> 00:13:32.560
readout

00:13:32.560 --> 00:13:33.829
of your account, and it's saying

00:13:33.839 --> 00:13:35.110
something totally different than what

00:13:35.120 --> 00:13:37.750
you wanted it to say. I'm not moved by

00:13:37.760 --> 00:13:40.470
what I see. I'm not moved by what I

00:13:40.480 --> 00:13:42.230
feel. I'm moved by what the word of God

00:13:42.240 --> 00:13:45.110
says. So, all of a sudden, you're

00:13:45.120 --> 00:13:47.110
looking at that and that bank

00:13:47.120 --> 00:13:48.870
account's yelling louder than your

00:13:48.880 --> 00:13:50.389
circumstance.

00:13:50.399 --> 00:13:52.790
The Bible says that my God shall supply

00:13:52.800 --> 00:13:54.790
all my needs according to his

00:13:54.800 --> 00:13:57.030
riches in glory by Christ Jesus and I

00:13:57.040 --> 00:13:58.550
have seed in the ground. I'm a tither

00:13:58.560 --> 00:14:01.509
and I have tither's rights. I believe

00:14:01.519 --> 00:14:04.150
that my God is going to take care of me.

00:14:04.160 --> 00:14:06.710
How many times that we've been there

00:14:06.720 --> 00:14:08.949
at the end when you get to the end

00:14:08.959 --> 00:14:11.110
of your paycheck and

00:14:11.120 --> 00:14:13.509
you've got a whole week ahead and you're

00:14:13.519 --> 00:14:16.310
going, Well,

00:14:16.320 --> 00:14:18.150
what are we going to do now? We're

00:14:18.160 --> 00:14:20.230
going to trust God.

00:14:20.240 --> 00:14:22.949
We're going to believe God.

00:14:22.959 --> 00:14:25.509
But there's only $25 left in the

00:14:25.519 --> 00:14:28.150
account. You only got $25 and we got

00:14:28.160 --> 00:14:30.150
these three kids and you got

00:14:30.150 --> 00:14:30.160
it.

00:14:30.160 --> 00:14:32.550
What are you going to do? You're

00:14:32.560 --> 00:14:34.949
going to trust God. That's whenever you

00:14:34.959 --> 00:14:37.030
better have a

00:14:37.030 --> 00:14:37.040
word

00:14:37.040 --> 00:14:38.870
to know

00:14:38.880 --> 00:14:41.750
that you're fully persuaded.

00:14:41.760 --> 00:14:43.750
I'm not just a believer that

00:14:43.760 --> 00:14:45.750
God's going to take care of me. I'm

00:14:45.760 --> 00:14:48.470
fully persuaded that God said he would

00:14:48.480 --> 00:14:50.790
supply all my needs.

00:14:50.800 --> 00:14:53.990
I'm a tither. I'm a giver. I'm a seer. And

00:14:54.000 --> 00:14:56.949
I'm a believer. But I'm fully persuaded

00:14:56.959 --> 00:14:58.790
now.

00:14:58.800 --> 00:15:00.389
And there's so many people that don't

00:15:00.399 --> 00:15:02.550
know how to go from believing to fully

00:15:02.560 --> 00:15:04.230
persuaded.

00:15:04.240 --> 00:15:06.949
What do you do whenever the doctor gives

00:15:06.959 --> 00:15:08.550
you a bad report and they tell you your

00:15:08.560 --> 00:15:09.829
daughter is never going to come out of

00:15:09.839 --> 00:15:12.150
it and she'll be in diapers the

00:15:12.160 --> 00:15:14.870
rest of her life and she'll never live a

00:15:14.880 --> 00:15:16.949
normal life. She'll never probably ever

00:15:16.959 --> 00:15:19.350
talk. You'll be blessed if she just is

00:15:19.360 --> 00:15:24.470
able to look you in the eye one day.

00:15:24.480 --> 00:15:25.829
What do you do whenever they give you

00:15:25.839 --> 00:15:27.590
that death sentence? Basically

00:15:27.600 --> 00:15:28.870
whenever it comes to all your dreams

00:15:28.880 --> 00:15:31.670
that you had for your child

00:15:31.680 --> 00:15:33.670
or maybe in some of your cases you've

00:15:33.680 --> 00:15:35.590
had a death sentence and they tell you

00:15:35.600 --> 00:15:36.790
you're going to die in the next couple

00:15:36.800 --> 00:15:38.389
months. You only have so

00:15:38.399 --> 00:15:40.949
much time to live.

00:15:40.959 --> 00:15:42.790
That's whenever the circumstance

00:15:42.790 --> 00:15:42.800
is

00:15:42.800 --> 00:15:46.230
yelling so loud at you and fear tries to

00:15:46.240 --> 00:15:49.430
set in. And fear tolerated is faith

00:15:49.440 --> 00:15:52.310
contaminated. Going over that inside of

00:15:52.320 --> 00:15:54.870
your head, you have the voice

00:15:54.880 --> 00:15:57.269
that yells louder at night of that fear

00:15:57.279 --> 00:15:58.710
and that roaring lion, you're going to

00:15:58.720 --> 00:16:00.790
die. You're never going to have a normal

00:16:00.800 --> 00:16:02.710
life. Things are never going to change

00:16:02.720 --> 00:16:06.470
for you. This is it, buddy. Tomorrow

00:16:06.480 --> 00:16:10.310
might be your last day.

00:16:10.320 --> 00:16:12.470
But I know what the word says, and I

00:16:12.480 --> 00:16:14.150
stand on the word. And you say, Well,

00:16:14.160 --> 00:16:16.790
what if you die? Well, I

00:16:16.800 --> 00:16:19.189
went out fighting.

00:16:19.199 --> 00:16:24.470
I went out standing.

00:16:24.480 --> 00:16:26.230
I'd rather be

00:16:26.240 --> 00:16:27.749
fighting on the good side and

00:16:27.759 --> 00:16:29.350
telling the devil he's a liar and

00:16:29.360 --> 00:16:33.269
going against it and

00:16:33.279 --> 00:16:35.749
go home that way than sit down and

00:16:35.749 --> 00:16:35.759
be

00:16:35.759 --> 00:16:37.509
in fear cuddled in a fetal

00:16:37.519 --> 00:16:42.389
position rocking.

00:16:42.399 --> 00:16:45.430
And so I've seen people

00:16:45.440 --> 00:16:48.230
that have believed and they went home.

00:16:48.240 --> 00:16:50.310
But guess what? They're on the victory

00:16:50.320 --> 00:16:53.670
side. Even on the other side, even if

00:16:53.680 --> 00:16:56.069
you didn't get your full

00:16:56.079 --> 00:16:57.990
manifestation of what you're believing

00:16:58.000 --> 00:17:00.790
for on this side of the earth,

00:17:00.800 --> 00:17:02.230
you're living and walking in

00:17:02.240 --> 00:17:03.910
victory at the moment. To be absent from

00:17:03.920 --> 00:17:05.829
the body is to be present with

00:17:05.839 --> 00:17:10.789
the Lord. You still are victorious

00:17:10.799 --> 00:17:13.270
regardless if you saw it here or

00:17:13.280 --> 00:17:14.230
you're going to get your full

00:17:14.240 --> 00:17:16.069
manifestation over there. Either way,

00:17:16.079 --> 00:17:20.470
you're a winner.

00:17:20.480 --> 00:17:22.069
And there's so many people that get

00:17:22.079 --> 00:17:24.230
caught up on all that.

00:17:25.679 --> 00:17:27.270
I've been around it all my life, it

00:17:27.270 --> 00:17:27.280
seems

00:17:27.280 --> 00:17:29.190
like now. And you watch and

00:17:29.200 --> 00:17:30.950
see some sister who was believing God

00:17:30.960 --> 00:17:32.710
for a healing and she didn't get it. You

00:17:32.720 --> 00:17:34.710
say, "Well, does God always

00:17:34.710 --> 00:17:34.720
heal?"I

00:17:34.720 --> 00:17:37.190
believe it.

00:17:37.200 --> 00:17:39.909
I believe God's a healer.

00:17:39.919 --> 00:17:42.630
I believe God's a deliverer.

00:17:42.640 --> 00:17:46.070
I believe I'm fully persuaded that my

00:17:46.080 --> 00:17:48.230
God is a healer

00:17:48.240 --> 00:17:50.150
either on this side or the other side. I

00:17:50.160 --> 00:17:52.710
know there's no sickness in heaven.

00:17:52.720 --> 00:17:56.470
There's no sickness and disease

00:17:56.480 --> 00:17:58.950
in heaven. He can't give you something

00:17:58.960 --> 00:18:01.190
he doesn't have over there. A

00:18:01.200 --> 00:18:02.390
lot of people say, "Well, did God put

00:18:02.400 --> 00:18:03.909
sickness on you?"God doesn't put

00:18:03.919 --> 00:18:06.630
sickness on people. I don't believe it.

00:18:06.640 --> 00:18:08.390
The devil comes to kill, steal, and

00:18:08.400 --> 00:18:10.310
destroy. The Lord said, "I have

00:18:10.320 --> 00:18:12.150
come that you might have life and life

00:18:12.160 --> 00:18:14.950
more

00:18:14.950 --> 00:18:14.960
abundantly."God

00:18:14.960 --> 00:18:18.470
doesn't put sickness on people.

00:18:18.480 --> 00:18:21.510
I do not believe that. We live in a

00:18:21.520 --> 00:18:24.870
fallen world and things happen,

00:18:24.880 --> 00:18:26.549
but I don't believe that God and the

00:18:26.559 --> 00:18:29.270
devil are working as buddies putting

00:18:29.280 --> 00:18:31.510
stuff on people.

00:18:33.280 --> 00:18:36.150
He was off balance here.

00:18:36.150 --> 00:18:36.160
I'll

00:18:36.160 --> 00:18:39.909
let him have a little cancer.

00:18:39.919 --> 00:18:42.070
Satan and him are not buddying up,

00:18:42.080 --> 00:18:43.909
slapping his bride around, slapping the

00:18:43.919 --> 00:18:45.669
church around, slapping people around. I

00:18:45.679 --> 00:18:47.750
don't believe it.

00:18:47.760 --> 00:18:52.230
You'll never convince me of it.

00:18:52.240 --> 00:18:54.150
The Bible says that God has come that we

00:18:54.160 --> 00:18:56.150
might have life and life more

00:18:56.160 --> 00:19:00.070
abundantly.

00:19:00.080 --> 00:19:01.669
What about your daughter Megan? What

00:19:01.679 --> 00:19:03.750
about that? That was my own stupid

00:19:03.760 --> 00:19:05.350
fault.

00:19:05.350 --> 00:19:05.360
He

00:19:05.360 --> 00:19:07.029
told me not to get the flu shot

00:19:07.039 --> 00:19:10.549
whenever I did it. Her Apgar scores

00:19:10.559 --> 00:19:12.950
were completely normal. She was

00:19:12.960 --> 00:19:15.510
starting to talk, doing

00:19:15.520 --> 00:19:17.510
everything. And within just

00:19:17.520 --> 00:19:20.070
a couple weeks

00:19:20.080 --> 00:19:23.029
of getting that flu vaccination, she ran

00:19:23.039 --> 00:19:26.630
a high fever and she lost all talking.

00:19:26.640 --> 00:19:30.870
Within just a couple weeks,

00:19:30.880 --> 00:19:33.270
she stopped looking at us in the eyes.

00:19:33.280 --> 00:19:35.430
She started looking over and being in

00:19:35.430 --> 00:19:35.440
la-la

00:19:35.440 --> 00:19:38.150
land. It was awful.

00:19:38.160 --> 00:19:40.630
And I'll never forget getting that

00:19:40.640 --> 00:19:43.990
letter in the mail certified

00:19:44.000 --> 00:19:46.070
from the doctor firing us as patients,

00:19:46.070 --> 00:19:46.080
telling

00:19:46.080 --> 00:19:47.590
us not to come back because we were

00:19:47.600 --> 00:19:49.190
saying we believe it's the flu

00:19:49.200 --> 00:19:50.470
vaccines. We believe all these things.

00:19:50.480 --> 00:19:52.630
She said don't come back. She fired us

00:19:52.640 --> 00:19:54.470
as patients and wouldn't let it

00:19:54.480 --> 00:19:55.909
go. I remember getting that

00:19:55.919 --> 00:19:58.230
FedEx letter

00:19:58.240 --> 00:20:00.470
in an envelope. Diana opened it up

00:20:00.480 --> 00:20:02.789
and said

00:20:02.799 --> 00:20:05.029
all that stuff that I'm not going to say

00:20:05.039 --> 00:20:06.549
because I end up slipping and saying her

00:20:06.559 --> 00:20:08.789
name.

00:20:08.799 --> 00:20:13.270
But all that to be said,

00:20:13.280 --> 00:20:16.070
at that point I didn't know what to do

00:20:16.080 --> 00:20:20.390
as a father because I was just young

00:20:20.400 --> 00:20:23.110
and I was so scared to even call it

00:20:23.120 --> 00:20:25.990
autism. I'll never forget when my mom came

00:20:25.990 --> 00:20:26.000
and

00:20:26.000 --> 00:20:28.549
because in my mind I knew

00:20:28.559 --> 00:20:31.590
Megan wasn't doing very well at the time.

00:20:31.600 --> 00:20:33.510
My mom took me out to this

00:20:33.520 --> 00:20:35.190
Mexican restaurant and

00:20:35.190 --> 00:20:35.200
she

00:20:35.200 --> 00:20:37.430
said, "Brandon, I need to tell you

00:20:37.440 --> 00:20:41.430
something."I

00:20:41.440 --> 00:20:43.350
remember looking at her thinking,

00:20:43.350 --> 00:20:43.360
"Well,

00:20:43.360 --> 00:20:45.990
what are you talking about?"She goes,

00:20:46.000 --> 00:20:47.750
"The family's been talking and we want to

00:20:47.760 --> 00:20:49.669
tell you we really believe that

00:20:49.679 --> 00:20:53.669
your Megan has

00:20:53.669 --> 00:20:53.679
autism."I

00:20:53.679 --> 00:20:59.190
lost it. I'm talking, fear hit me

00:20:59.200 --> 00:21:01.750
like a 2x4 upside the head. It felt

00:21:01.760 --> 00:21:03.270
like

00:21:03.270 --> 00:21:03.280
that.

00:21:03.280 --> 00:21:05.270
I remember thinking I felt

00:21:05.280 --> 00:21:07.430
so betrayed at the time, so upset

00:21:07.440 --> 00:21:09.830
because it had gone on for so long. And

00:21:09.840 --> 00:21:11.669
people didn't know how to really address

00:21:11.679 --> 00:21:14.310
it. I guess my mom and dad didn't know

00:21:14.320 --> 00:21:16.789
how to really address it because I was

00:21:16.799 --> 00:21:19.590
just naive. First child, we

00:21:19.600 --> 00:21:21.990
didn't know what we were doing really.

00:21:22.000 --> 00:21:24.549
But we didn't realize how far behind

00:21:24.559 --> 00:21:29.909
Megan was and her not talking at

00:21:29.919 --> 00:21:32.470
three years old. What was

00:21:32.480 --> 00:21:34.149
over that and started looking at things

00:21:34.159 --> 00:21:37.110
and going

00:21:37.110 --> 00:21:37.120
through

00:21:37.120 --> 00:21:40.149
her development out of just ignorance.

00:21:40.159 --> 00:21:42.149
We didn't realize

00:21:42.159 --> 00:21:43.669
what was going on until family started

00:21:43.679 --> 00:21:45.270
shedding light on it because

00:21:45.280 --> 00:21:48.710
of my sister's kids.

00:21:48.720 --> 00:21:52.149
As I look back at those days,

00:21:52.159 --> 00:21:54.390
it was the hardest time of my life. But

00:21:54.400 --> 00:21:57.909
if it wasn't for the word of God,

00:21:57.919 --> 00:22:00.470
if it wasn't for knowing who I am in

00:22:00.480 --> 00:22:02.310
Christ,

00:22:02.320 --> 00:22:04.950
when I came home and started talking to

00:22:04.960 --> 00:22:07.909
Diana that night, she wept and wept and

00:22:07.919 --> 00:22:10.710
wept.

00:22:10.720 --> 00:22:12.789
We took her to a doctor and I can't

00:22:12.799 --> 00:22:14.630
even say his name because he was not. Dr.

00:22:14.640 --> 00:22:17.430
Edgington was his name and he was a

00:22:17.430 --> 00:22:17.440
neuropsychologist.

00:22:17.440 --> 00:22:21.590
Dr. Edgington

00:22:21.600 --> 00:22:24.950
and

00:22:24.960 --> 00:22:27.669
he was in Edmond, Oklahoma. He was only

00:22:27.679 --> 00:22:30.149
one of so many in the whole area. It took

00:22:30.159 --> 00:22:33.430
us forever to get in there.

00:22:35.600 --> 00:22:37.669
I'll never forget his report that first

00:22:37.679 --> 00:22:39.510
time he went in there and he evaluated

00:22:39.520 --> 00:22:42.470
her. I felt like somebody

00:22:42.480 --> 00:22:45.110
had just kicked the snot out of

00:22:45.120 --> 00:22:48.070
me. I walked away just weeping.

00:22:48.080 --> 00:22:51.029
So angry at the circumstance. So angry.

00:22:51.039 --> 00:22:54.549
So afraid because I didn't want anybody

00:22:54.559 --> 00:22:57.270
saying the word, because life and death is in

00:22:57.280 --> 00:22:59.750
the power of your tongue. I was

00:22:59.760 --> 00:23:02.149
so scared for anybody to say out of

00:23:02.159 --> 00:23:05.029
their mouth that Megan had autism

00:23:05.039 --> 00:23:06.789
because I didn't want them speaking it.

00:23:06.799 --> 00:23:07.990
I didn't want them to speak word

00:23:08.000 --> 00:23:09.190
curses. I didn't want to speak

00:23:09.200 --> 00:23:12.070
anything because I was so freaked out by

00:23:12.080 --> 00:23:14.230
the power of life and death in

00:23:14.240 --> 00:23:15.830
your tongue and speaking things over

00:23:15.840 --> 00:23:18.230
her. I wouldn't allow anybody to say

00:23:18.240 --> 00:23:21.669
anything.

00:23:21.679 --> 00:23:23.830
So does it sound flaky now? Yeah.

00:23:23.840 --> 00:23:29.190
Because of what I've walked through.

00:23:29.200 --> 00:23:31.590
There's so much that you feel like

00:23:31.600 --> 00:23:33.270
it's bondage. I look at it back and I say

00:23:33.280 --> 00:23:35.270
there's a lot of bondage in that. The

00:23:35.280 --> 00:23:39.830
way I had to come to

00:23:39.840 --> 00:23:42.950
the reality of what I was

00:23:42.960 --> 00:23:45.270
looking at. There was so much

00:23:45.280 --> 00:23:49.110
bondage, but

00:23:49.120 --> 00:23:50.950
God has brought us through is

00:23:50.960 --> 00:23:54.310
what I'm trying to tell you all.

00:23:54.320 --> 00:23:56.630
We're still seeing healing even today.

00:23:56.640 --> 00:23:59.510
We're seeing manifestations of her

00:23:59.520 --> 00:24:02.710
changing and yet she's

00:24:02.720 --> 00:24:04.630
in her 20s.

00:24:08.000 --> 00:24:09.350
And I'm going to say something that's

00:24:09.360 --> 00:24:11.669
very private, personal, but when she's

00:24:11.679 --> 00:24:13.750
getting ready to start her cycle now,

00:24:13.760 --> 00:24:15.510
she knows when she started and she'll

00:24:15.520 --> 00:24:18.630
get stuff to make sure she doesn't

00:24:18.640 --> 00:24:21.110
mess up the house.

00:24:21.120 --> 00:24:24.230
She knows now when her cycle has

00:24:24.240 --> 00:24:26.390
started

00:24:26.400 --> 00:24:29.750
and she goes and cleans herself

00:24:29.760 --> 00:24:35.990
up.

00:24:36.000 --> 00:24:38.230
If anybody understands a child with

00:24:38.240 --> 00:24:41.750
autism, that is a miracle in itself.

00:24:41.760 --> 00:24:45.510
And it took years

00:24:45.520 --> 00:24:48.230
of believing that she wouldn't play in

00:24:48.240 --> 00:24:50.549
her

